FilterByTime - Class in Filters
This is the Explain how to work with the filter: in some class (like Main) run that line --> FilterByTime.filter("2017-10-27 16:16:36", "2017-10-27 16:17:11"); that line will sort all elements between the time +1 second s.t the time 2017-10-27 16:16:36 will not collect, only from the time 2017-10-27 16:16:37 will be inserted to the collection.
